      <div class="SOTTO_PARA"><a name="DUC094c1508251810058fa98beb784d42d2"></a>Refitting the idler and tensioner pulley mounting pins
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e12713"> </a>Apply the recommended threadlocker to the pin thread.
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e12715"> </a>Insert the tensioner pins (1) on the heads, and screw them by means of tool (A) no. <span class="bold">88713.1821</span>.
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e12720"> </a>Tighten the tensioner pins to a torque of 50 Nm (Min. 45 Nm - Max. 55 Nm).
         </div>
